---
title: Seared Rosemary, Honey & Mustard Chicken with Kumara Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: Dinner tonight proves, once and for all, why honey and mustard is a winning combo. Just add a pinch of garlic
and a little rosemary, and you get a glaze that's so sublime you'll be scraping up every last bit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-seared-rosemary-honey-mustard-chicken-4b24fd4b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/seared-rosemary-honey-mustard-chicken-603c6a6ba4209516833ea12a-4c2a6ed2.pdf
